Description: I made a presentation about literacy using Prezi. This is a tool that helps me make presentations on the internet. My presentation is about what digital literacy's why it is important in the world we live in today.
It talks about things like using tools and being safe on the internet. It also talks about being responsible when I'm online.
Digital literacy is not about using computers and phones. It is also about thinking and making good choices when I am online. I need to be able to look at information on the internet and figure out what is true and what is not. I also need to be able to talk to people in a way when I am online. Digital literacy is important for doing in school and getting a good job. It is also important for being a part of the world we live in today.
My presentation looks nice. Is easy to follow. It has parts that are easy to see and it is not too hard to understand. I like using Prezi because it lets me make my presentation interesting. It has a way of zooming in and out that makes my presentation more like a story.. Sometimes it was hard for me to make sure everything made sense because it does not go in a straight line. Making this presentation helped me get better at showing people information in a way that's easy to understand and nice to look at. I learned more, about literacy and how to use Prezi to make my presentations better.
